{"type": "article", "id": 23197, "title": "3D 打印饰品", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-03T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125707j3tqIgYOFeKlSNJX.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">KWAMBIO 是纽约一家提供定制 3D 打印产品的网站，目前已联合 18 位设计师或设计组合提供超过 10 组产品。他们的设计不再是塑料一样的零件，而是具有审美价值的陶瓷物件或金属首饰。比如纽约设计师 Andrew Sack 带来的具有笔筒功能的花瓶，外形有点像古典园林中的梅花窗，具有装饰性。<a href=\"http://kwambio.com/\">这里是网站的链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125705QbUxP47RzkTdnK2F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125705JHIcg1Ul7kjO94Sn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125706Hzt5QZuSfG0pDVqR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125706IlvmT5KLOWgeoSuw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125707oKLS8WfepazRQHrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}